{[#] The game continued:} 22... d5 23. cxd5 exd5 24. e5 Nfe4 25. Re3 $5 Bxe5
26. b4 Bxd4 $5 27. Qxd4 Ne6 28. Qxb6 {Black now needs to prepare ...d5-d4 by
