({Neutral play tends to allow ...f7-f5.} 14. Rac1 f5 15. Nd2 Bf6 16. Qd3 Ne5
17. Qc2 Ng4 18. Nf1 Qc7 $11 19. Qa4 $2 {Foygel,I (2474)-Vucic,M (2396) Seattle
