(23. cxb5 Nxf3 24. Kxf3 d5 $40 {/\...dxe4+, ><Qd2, Kf3, /\...d4, >< Nc3, e3.})
23... Nxf3 $1 $146 {Ruining the whole white kingside structure. White could
not have taken half-measures as in the game.} ({Right after sacrificing the
pawn I had a long thought. I considered that the knight sacrifices on e4 or f3
should have equal merits, but eventually decided that the consequences of the
