whether the opponent is forced to accept it!} 23... Nxe4 $2 {This move does
not cause any structural damage so White is not forced to capture at all.} 24.
Qe2 $1 $16 {A move out of the blue - suddenly Black's position is hanging. I
had to make use of all my tricking resources to save the game. Skembris,S 
(2525)-Marin,M (2520) Moscow 1994 (½-½, 46).}) 24. Nxd6 (24. Kxf3 Nxe4 25.
Qe1 Nc3+ 26. Kf2 Nxd1+ 27. Qxd1 Bxb2 28. Rxb2 d5 $36) 24... Rxd6 25. Qxd6 Nxe4
26. Qd7 $1 Ne1+ (26... Qa8 27. Ra1) 27. Kg1 Nf3+ 28. Kg2 $11 {A draw may look
